Context: World Teachers' Day is celebrated on October 5 at George Brown College. Students are encouraged to express their appreciation for their professors and instructors by sharing stories of positive impact and support. Submissions can be anonymous and will be featured on the college website (georgebrown.ca). The phone number for inquiries is 416-415-2000, and TTY number is 1-877-515-5559. The email address to contact is ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The college's social media hub can be visited for more information. The information on the website is subject to change without notice, and students are responsible for verifying fee requirements.
